- id: 1218-kdp-word-search-puzzles-word-lists
  title: KDP Word Search Puzzles (Word Lists)
  tags:
  - writing
  - kdp
  - word
  - search
  - puzzles
  - lists
  family: writing
  body: 'I want yout to create an ordered list of words in language [TARGETLANGUAGE]
    up to 100 words. Make sure the words are arranged in an alphabetical order. Also,
    make sure no single word is added twice. Create a list of words about this: [PROMPT]'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
